{"lemma":"مَثابَة","slug":"مَثابَة","root":"ث.#.ب","root_slug":"ث-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ث-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَثابَة","root":"ثوب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4814"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%AB%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"refuge, resort"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place from the root ث و ب (ṯ w b)."},"ipa":["/ma.θaː.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4814","headword_ar":"مَثَابَةٌ","root":"vwb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(accord. to Aboo-Is-hák originally ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavowabapN","text_ar":"مَثْوَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", T)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place to which people return,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, Aboo-Is-hák, T, S, Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to which one returns,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time after time;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbN","text_ar":"مَثَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same: (Aboo-Is-hák, T:) and the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of assembly"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"congregation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place where people assemble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"congregate, after they have separated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓ the latter word: (M, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of alighting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode; an abode;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a house;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the inhabitants thereof return to it (ISh, S) after having gone to their affairs: (S:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbaAtN","text_ar":"مَثَابَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [also mentioned above as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbN","text_ar":"مَثَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] (ISh;) or it is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbN","text_ar":"مَثَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;) [or this is a coll. gen. n.;] or, accord. to Fr and others,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAabapN","text_ar":"مَثَاَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbN","text_ar":"مَثَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"are the same: Th says that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":",) is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbapN","text_ar":"مَثَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and some say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavowabapN","text_ar":"مَثْوَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but no one reads thus [in the Kur]. (TA.) It has the first of all these meanings in the Kur ii. 119: (T, S, Bd, Jel, TA:) or it there means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of recompense"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reward"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the pilgrimage to the Kaabeh and the visitation thereof. (Bd.) ―         -b2-  And, sometimes, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place where the hunter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fowler, puts his snare."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbapN Albiy^ori","text_ar":"مَثَابَةٌ البِيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The place where the water of the well collects:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place reached by the water of the well when it returns and collects after one has drawn from it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~ato mavaAbapu jaholihi","text_ar":"جَمَّتْ مَثَابَةُ جَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His ignorance became confirmed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna yasotajim~u mavaAbapa safahihi","text_ar":"كَانَ يَسْتَجِمُّ مَثَابَةَ سَفَهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He used to wait for his lightwittedness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silliness, to attain its full degree"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: a metaphorical phrase, occurring in a trad. (Har p. 68.) ―         -b4-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stones that project,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overhang, around the well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which the man sometimes stands in order that the bucket"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dalow","text_ar":"دَلْو"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garob","text_ar":"غَرْب"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may not strike against the side of the well:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place where it is walled round within"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoDiEu","text_ar":"مَوْضِعُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ihaA","text_ar":"طَيِّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (K:) or, accord. to IAar, it means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaY~u","text_ar":"طَىُّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albiy^ori","text_ar":"البِيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but [ISd says,] I know not whether he mean thereby"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoDiEu Tay~ihaA","text_ar":"مَوْضِعُ طَيِّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the building it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walling it round within"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with stones;"},{"kind":"text","text":"though it is rarely that a word of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafaEalapN","text_ar":"مَفَعَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mvAbp","text_ar":"مثابة"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is an inf. n. (M.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbN","text_ar":"مَثَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see what is said of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tavowiybN","text_ar":"تَثْوِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the last sentence of the second paragraph of art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vrb","text_ar":"ثرب"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mavaAbaAtN","text_ar":"مَثَابَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the pl.] also signifies (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foundations of a house."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vawaAbN","text_ar":"ثَوَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["ISh","S","Msb","M","K","T","Bd","Jel","TA","A"]}]}}